@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Get Context

skinparam defaultFontSize 11

actor User
participant "AI Controller" as Controller #Gold
participant "RAG Context Service" as RAGContext #LightGreen
participant "OpenAI Embeddings" as Embeddings #Pink
participant "Supabase" as Supabase #Orange

User -> Controller: POST /ai/context\n(Query + Project ID)

Controller -> RAGContext: getRAGContext()

RAGContext -> Embeddings: Generate query embedding

RAGContext -> Supabase: Cosine similarity search
Supabase --> RAGContext: Top k chunks\n(sorted by relevance)

RAGContext --> Controller: Context chunks
Controller --> User: JSON Response\n{ query, context }

@enduml
